            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
                <strong>‚úàÔ∏è Book Flights</strong><br>
                Find and book domestic and international flights
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
                <strong>üöó Rent Vehicles</strong><br>
                Rent cars and explore the islands at your own pace
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
